      <title>Kelleher警告瑞银面临“极端” 50％的资本需求增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/kelleher-warns-ubs-faces-extreme-50-rise-in-capital-demands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团（UBS Group AG）主席科尔姆·凯勒赫（Colm Kelleher）表示，瑞士目前的改革计划将大大提高银行的资本要求，因为他试图表明此举将有效地使全球公司的竞争力变得不竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/kelleher-warns-ubs-faces-extreme-50-rise-in-capital-demands</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 09:13:38 GMT</pubDate>
