      <title>在气体市场动荡中，丹斯克商品的利润跌落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/danske-commodities-2024-profit-falls-on-easing-market-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Danske商品A/S表示，去年的利润下降了近50％，因为越来越多的地缘政治风险使欧洲的天然气市场难以交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/danske-commodities-2024-profit-falls-on-easing-market-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 06:53:04 GMT</pubDate>
